//HOME STRINGS Start Stop Welcome to BirdUp!

Curious about birdsongs and what song belongs to what bird? BirdUp can help you find out by recording the birdsong and recognizing up to 50 bird species found across Europe. 
Simply record the song and the app will do the rest.

Now go out and discover some of nature's best singers!
